---
title: Creamy Butternut-Sage Penne with Crispy Bacon
description: Mashed butternut squash is the backbone of tonight's creamy sage sauce, which drapes over penne and spinach for a meal that delivers on richness without feeling heavy. Pan-fried crispy bacon gives each bite a delicious salty crunch!
